            <path d="m11.5 9.5 2-2"></path>
            <path d="m8.5 6.5 2-2"></path>
            <path d="m17.5 15.5 2-2"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="size-guide-header__title">GUÍA DE TALLES</h1>
      </div>
      <p class="size-guide-header__subtitle">
        Encontrá el talle perfecto para tu camiseta
      </p>
    </div>

    {%- comment %} Size Table {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="size-guide-table-section">
      <div class="size-guide-table-wrapper">
        <div class="size-guide-table-scroll">
          <table class="size-guide-table">
            <thead>
              <tr class="size-guide-table__header-row">
                <th class="size-guide-table__header">TALLE</th>
                <th class="size-guide-table__header">PECHO (CM)</th>
                <th class="size-guide-table__header">ANCHO (CM)</th>
                <th class="size-guide-table__header">LARGO (CM)</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="size-guide-table__row">
                <td class="size-guide-table__cell size-guide-table__cell--size">S</td>
                <td class="size-guide-table__cell">88-96</td>
                <td class="size-guide-table__cell">49</td>
                <td class="size-guide-table__cell">68</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="size-guide-table__row">
                <td class="size-guide-table__cell size-guide-table__cell--size">M</td>
                <td class="size-guide-table__cell">96-104</td>
                <td class="size-guide-table__cell">52</td>
                <td class="size-guide-table__cell">70</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="size-guide-table__row">
                <td class="size-guide-table__cell size-guide-table__cell--size">L</td>
                <td class="size-guide-table__cell">104-112</td>
                <td class="size-guide-table__cell">55</td>
                <td class="size-guide-table__cell">72</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="size-guide-table__row">
                <td class="size-guide-table__cell size-guide-table__cell--size">XL</td>
                <td class="size-guide-table__cell">112-120</td>
                <td class="size-guide-table__cell">58</td>
                <td class="size-guide-table__cell">74</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="size-guide-table__row">
                <td class="size-guide-table__cell size-guide-table__cell--size">XXL</td>
                <td class="size-guide-table__cell">120-128</td>
                <td class="size-guide-table__cell">61</td>
                <td class="size-guide-table__cell">76</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {%- comment %} Info Cards Grid {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="size-guide-info-grid">
      {%- comment %} Como Medir Card {%- endcomment -%}
      <div class="size-guide-card">
        <div class="size-guide-card__header">
          <svg class="size-guide-card__icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M21.3 15.3a2.4 2.4 0 0 1 0 3.4l-2.6 2.6a2.4 2.4 0 0 1-3.4 0L2.7 8.7a2.41 2.41 0 0 1 0-3.4l2.6-2.6a2.41 2.41 0 0 1 3.4 0Z"></path>
            <path d="m14.5 12.5 2-2"></path>
            <path d="m11.5 9.5 2-2"></path>
            <path d="m8.5 6.5 2-2"></path>
            <path d="m17.5 15.5 2-2"></path>
          </svg>
          <h2 class="size-guide-card__title">Cómo tomar tus medidas</h2>
        </div>
        <ol class="size-guide-steps">
          <li class="size-guide-step">
            <span class="size-guide-step__number">1</span>
            <div class="size-guide-step__content">
              <strong>Pecho:</strong> Medí el contorno de tu pecho en la parte más ancha, pasando la cinta por las axilas
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="size-guide-step">
            <span class="size-guide-step__number">2</span>
            <div class="size-guide-step__content">
              <strong>Ancho:</strong> Medí de hombro a hombro en la parte más ancha de tu espalda
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="size-guide-step">
            <span class="size-guide-step__number">3</span>
            <div class="size-guide-step__content">
              <strong>Largo:</strong> Medí desde el punto más alto del hombro hasta donde querés que llegue la camiseta
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="size-guide-step">
            <span class="size-guide-step__number">4</span>
            <div class="size-guide-step__content">
              Para mayor precisión, tomá las medidas sobre una camiseta que te quede bien
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="size-guide-step">
            <span class="size-guide-step__number">5</span>
            <div class="size-guide-step__content">
              Compará tus medidas con la tabla de arriba para encontrar tu talle ideal
            </div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      {%- comment %} Consejos Card {%- endcomment -%}
      <div class="size-guide-card">
        <div class="size-guide-card__header">
          <svg class="size-guide-card__icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
            <path d="M12 16v-4"></path>
